<p class="hm_sub_ttl">Welcome to Apex Venture Partners </p>
<p class="hm_left_txt">Apex Venture Partners, established in 1987, is one of the oldest venture capital 
firms in Mid-America. The firm has invested in over 150 companies throughout the 
United States. <br />
<br />
Apex&#39;s guiding investment philosophy is to provide exceptional returns for our 
investors by partnering with entrepreneurs and executives to build significant 
value in their companies.</p>
</div>


		
