<p class="hm_sm"><strong>Current fund:</strong> Apex VI (2007), $140 million</p>
<p class="hm_sm"><strong>Stage focus:</strong> Seed to growth stage</p>
<p class="hm_sm"><strong>Investment size:</strong> $200K to $6 million initially</p>
<p class="hm_sm"><strong>Industry focus: </strong>Technology-enabled services (consumer &amp; business), information 
technology, and clean technology sectors</p>
<p class="hm_sm"><strong>Geographic focus:</strong> North America</p></div>


